{
    "title": "Aint Too Proud To Beg",
    "artist": "The Rolling Stones",
    "composer": "",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 1]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I know you wanna leave me,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I refuse to let you go,</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If I have to beg, plead for your sympathy,</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I don&#x27;t mind &#x27;cause you mean that much to me.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to beg   sweet darlin&#x27;,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me don&#x27;t you go,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to plead, baby, baby,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me, don&#x27;t you go.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 2]</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Now I&#x27;ve heard a cryin&#x27; man</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Is half a man with no sense of pride,</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">But if I have to cry to keep you,</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I don&#x27;t mind weepin&#x27; if weepin&#x27;s gonna keep you by my side.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to beg   sweet darlin&#x27;,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me don&#x27;t you go,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to plead, baby, baby,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me, don&#x27;t you go.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 3]</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If I have to sleep on your doorstep all night and day</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Just to keep you from walking away,</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Let your friends laugh, even this I can stand,</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">&#x27;cause I wanna keep you any way I can.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to beg   sweet darlin&#x27;,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me don&#x27;t you go,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to plead, baby, baby,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me, don&#x27;t you go.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Guitar Solo]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 4]</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">NC              B                   E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Now I&#x27;ve got a love so deep in the pit of my heart,</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">And each day it grows more and more,</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I&#x27;m not ashamed to call and plead to you, baby,</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If pleading keeps you from walking out that door.</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to beg   sweet darlin&#x27;,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me don&#x27;t you go,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to plead, baby, baby,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me, don&#x27;t you go.</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ain&#x27;t too proud to beg   sweet darlin&#x27;,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Please don&#x27;t leave me don&#x27;t you go,</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=